Enum WordSuffixType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WordSuffixType>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<WordSuffixType>
    public enum WordSuffixType
extends Enum<WordSuffixType>
    Word suffix codes. Suffixes are applied to words after a '@' character.
